藥side effect 可能做嘢／諗野會有影響添<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nafter all, 睇完醫生乖乖地做rehab recover la 好返就可以返工x2046 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申: 可能係你將來嘅同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"448d9be2ae3cdec8beb0a01be4b4565aad609dab","tid":292634,"uid":69886,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T14:43:10.000Z","msg":"屌你 有精神病就咪撚做護士啦"},{"pid":"346b2a54eeb54c20c4c78ef726b1122387bfad77","tid":292634,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T14:43:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解唔係拎金卡,  之後喺依家個機構賴死唔走 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未畢業</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n年輕人,  既然你未入職,  我就唔教壞你,   唔講啲拎金卡既人既仆街野 <br />\n<br />\n但係反而 ... 你要學識睇化每樣事情 ,  仲好過睇精神科啦<br />\n<br />\n至於有公院精神科紀錄 係咪影響招聘 ,   無人敢答你真野架啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"085392aec8d33f330dcbf34514bb5010affd5dfe","tid":292634,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T14:45:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該就冇白紙黑字寫明話唔請嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇公立醫院嘅話，psy hx record應該都只會喺入職前同你body check 個staff先知（？）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過就算真係知你有psy hx，應該都係主要考慮你嘅functioning /in remission/ risk of relapse，睇你應唔應付到第日nurse 嘅工作 （或者而家返學出place）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 尤其是護士呢行stress level 咁高 +/- 你食藥side effect 可能做嘢／諗野會有影響添<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nafter all, 睇完醫生乖乖地做rehab recover la 好返就可以返工x2046 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申: 可能係你將來嘅同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我問你一樣野呀<br />